Speaker 1: Thank you for calling. This is John. How can I help you?

Speaker 2: Hey, John. How are you doing?

Speaker 1: Doing well. How can I help you?

Speaker 2: I ordered some Scorblue online.

Speaker 1: Yeah.

Speaker 2: And they sent me all the numbers and stuff.

Speaker 1: But I only pushed for the one-time thing, and it set me up for a prescription.

Speaker 2: And I just want to know if you can talk to my wife about it and figure out how to stop that. Okay?

Speaker 1: Okay. Let me get the right person to help with that, though, but we can help you with that. One second.
